        <num>CC 717</num>
        <heading>717.  Partition in kind</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 717.  Partition in kind.
If the estate owned in indivision is partitioned in kind, the servitude established by a co-owner on his undivided part burdens only the part allotted to him.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
